	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Butcher</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From The Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead Wiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><div class="mw-revision"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 04:00, 25 May 2020 by <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/User:Soyweiser" class="mw-userlink" title="User:Soyweiser"><bdi>Soyweiser</bdi></a> <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/User_talk:Soyweiser" class="mw-usertoollinks-talk" title="User talk:Soyweiser">talk</a> | <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Special:Contributions/Soyweiser" class="mw-usertoollinks-contribs" title="Special:Contributions/Soyweiser">contribs</a>)</span></div><div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Butcher&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=35539" title="Butcher">diff</a>) <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Butcher&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=35539" title="Butcher">← Older revision</a> | Latest revision (diff) | Newer revision → (diff)</div></div></div>
		
		
		
