		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p>Butchery is an important source of resources in <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/0.D_(Danny)" title="0.D (Danny)">0.D (Danny)</a>, such as <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Bone" title="Bone">bones</a>, <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Sinew" title="Sinew">sinews</a>, <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Bionic" class="mw-redirect" title="Bionic">bionics</a>, <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Raw_hide&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Raw hide (page does not exist)">hides</a>, <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Raw_pelt&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Raw pelt (page does not exist)">pelt</a>, <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Chunk_of_meat" title="Chunk of meat">meat</a>, and many other <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Raw_liver&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Raw liver (page does not exist)">edible</a> <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Raw_offal&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Raw offal (page does not exist)">organ</a> <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=Raw_brains&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Raw brains (page does not exist)">parts</a>. As an added bonus, all forms of butchery also prevent <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Zombie" title="Zombie">zombies</a> from coming back from the dead, but usually just <span style="background-color: #F0F0F0; color: #333333; width: 2em; border: 1px outset #666; border-radius: .3em; -moz-border-radius: .3em; -webkit-border-radius: .3em; margin:0; padding:1px 2px; clear:none; font-family:monospace; font-size:1.2em">s</span>mashing the corpses is less time-consuming.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
